mutation ($payload:OAuthCreateClientInput!)

		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthGetClients (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthFindClient (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	oAuthFindClientById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:OAuthUpdateClientInput!)
{
	oAuthUpdateClient (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	oAuthDeleteClientById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	oAuthDeleteClients (query: $query)
	{
		id
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
